{"tid":1133885,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[這趟旅行若算開心 亦是無負這一生] 大英帝國之旅","createTime":"2019-05-01T11:53:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T00:33:04.000Z","uid":119433,"like":56,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"c3eb6aa1559df37287f68a8f13372675a8589545","tid":1133885,"uid":119433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T11:53:36.000Z","msg":"BGM:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3aUuei4WOHw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3aUuei4WOHw&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgELPkHgDHOcRHwLuXI7BMvHI%3D&h=bb2dc0fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3aUuei4WOHw</a><br />\n<br />\n龍應台講過：不必懼怕孤獨，因為智慧必然來自孤獨。<br />\n<br />\n旗袍妹好細個嘅時候，旗袍爸已經帶子(女)雄狼，十幾年來，旗袍妹去過哂歐亞美澳咁多大洲，嘗盡各地風土人情，亦都結交唔少旅伴。旗袍爸本身讀文學，安排嘅景點都偏學術性，一日可以跑幾間博物館⋯⋯睇係好睇，但chur咗啲咯。<br />\n<br />\n讀咗六年傳統名校，兩年u，一直覺得人生根本就係受旗袍媽擺佈。中四開始就好想讀大學某一科，但係得償所願入咗去又如何？學業、人際、愛情、intern皆失，於是決定走兩個禮拜堂，去一個冇香港人嘅文明國家散下心。日本定歐洲好？既然走兩個禮拜，一於去遠啲，去英國。一來幾年前全家去過叫做認得路，二來旗袍妹淨係識雞腸唔識架文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己一個旅行，究竟係咩感覺？二十歲女啦，終於唔駛跟旗袍爸趕景點，又唔駛好似旗袍媽咁早瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諗起都興奮！但係出發前一晚先執喼，第二日上完堂直接去機場，第一次唔跟旗袍爸旗袍媽離開香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />心裡面總會戚戚然⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n旗袍妹家境唔好，啲錢用哂去浪跡天涯，冇錢買canon nikon。所有相都係蘋果出品，屌細力啲，旗袍妹得一塊西㗎咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每一個po旗袍妹都會配一首BGM，希望諸位巴絲會一路聽一路睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xqTPoFu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxqTPoFu.jpg&h=c5fdba79&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n為咗斷絕一切喺香港嘅聯繫，旗袍妹最初連上網卡都唔想買。但係旗袍爸硬係要塞過嚟，「冇，今朝行過深水埗，好平，去到記住whatsapp我哋⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ejdcmqx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEjdcmqx.jpg&h=fa1ee401&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n旗袍爸係旗袍妹臨出發前出咗張ae cx附屬卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 終於可以一嘗傳說中嘅機場魚蛋粉。好笑嘅係，講「魚蛋粉」啲廚師聽唔明，要講「fishball noodle soup」先得。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XAFez3d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXAFez3d.jpg&h=7d5c4630&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n又食又拎，典型香港人。旗袍妹話緊自己。好彩個lounge緊閘口，如果唔係，成個trip就凍過水㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/504i1vn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F504i1vn.jpg&h=80ed3738&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n由飛機俯瞰倫敦萬家燈火。其實係凌晨四點幾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dyW9oEM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdyW9oEM.jpg&h=e01bca15&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n一出機場，旗袍妹空虛、寂寞、凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3d865840e9bbf20f81253fbe496c881516ebd90","tid":1133885,"uid":134182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T12:12:54.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"73b1fed179cd174a8cfb0e548c318696a1aead49","tid":1133885,"uid":119433,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T13:32:15.000Z","msg":"BGM:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GgM5mqBgh18\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGgM5mqBgh18&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgELPkHgDHOcRHwLuXI7BMvHI%3D&h=ab8c60ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GgM5mqBgh18</a><br />\n<br />\n晏殊《蝶戀花》：「昨夜西風凋碧樹。獨上高樓，望盡天涯路。」<br />\n<br />\n倫敦Underground冇冷氣，百幾年嘅廢氣到依家都密閉喺黑鼆鼆嘅隧道裡面，就好似文天祥所寫嘅「水土之氣」。不過旗袍妹成24個鐘冇沖涼，有股「穢氣」，吾氣有一，以一敵眾，吾何患焉！<br />\n<br />\nWhatsapp:「你到咗未？」<br />\n<br />\n要嚟嘅始終要嚟。<br />\n<br />\n唔係旗袍爸，唔係旗袍媽，係佢。俾個名佢，叫N君啦。<br />\n<br />\n旗袍妹：「唔。太早落機，冇舖頭開門😢」<br />\nN：「依家英國幾多點？」<br />\n旗袍妹：「朝頭早6點12分。頭先喺飛機度冇乜點瞓過😭😭」<br />\n⋯⋯<br />\nN：「坐咗幾多個鐘頭機？」<br />\n旗袍妹：「12個鐘😭頭先坐中間位，俾兩個大肥婆夾住 😂」<br />\n⋯⋯<br />\n旗袍妹：「好肚餓🤢」<br />\nN：「咁快啲買嘢食啦」<br />\n⋯⋯<br />\nUnderground一入黑鼆鼆嘅隧道就收唔到電話，如夢如幻，若即若離。究竟我收唔到whatsapp嘅嗰幾分鐘，佢做緊啲咩呢？佢諗緊啲咩呢？<br />\n<br />\n不過上天好公平。呢幾分鐘，全車人都喺呢條川流不息嘅時光隧道進入漫長無止、不見天日嘅等待。<br />\n<br />\n應承咗自己返香港先處理佢，於是狠心做話題終結者。最尾求其揀咗喺Hyde Park Corner落車，揪住成30kg嘅喼同阿伯一齊做晨運。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o5nXycQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo5nXycQ.jpg&h=6081b227&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nWellington Arch<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r0gNaZy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr0gNaZy.jpg&h=eb74b76c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n海德公園內睹旭日初升。換著喺香港呢個時間，我應該都未瞓。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bxFVj03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbxFVj03.jpg&h=74195537&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n平時俾旗袍爸話唔識影相，呢張俾自己打下飛機先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DxgQTcR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDxgQTcR.jpg&h=cab48b50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食完pret早餐再行去Paddington，喼都爛埋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/05/01/212754_deaa043d14d1886598670c62fc683b9d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F01%2F212754_deaa043d14d1886598670c62fc683b9d.jpg&h=636a9388&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/43jOE5C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F43jOE5C.jpg&h=61851ba1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n上網search見到呢間嘢開，即刻仆過嚟過日晨。人總係犯賤嘅，忍唔到手買咗個Paddington Bear俾N君。"},{"pid":"60c6ad0686a71a12281281f5acb6b82ec708c214","tid":1133885,"uid":119433,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T16:48:43.000Z","msg":"BGM:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HG2UMO6rZd4?t=80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHG2UMO6rZd4%3Ft%3D80&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgELPkHgDHOcRHwLuXI7BMvHI%3D&h=935af01f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HG2UMO6rZd4?t=80</a><br />\n<br />\n柳永《鳳棲梧》：「衣帶漸寬終不悔，爲伊消得人憔悴。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xkm10Y1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxkm10Y1.jpg&h=c5cea39a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日出而作，倫敦市民搭Underground返工，我反而落得清閒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3vdouSo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3vdouSo.jpg&h=2214c21f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBaker Street 站月台，fabulously British。<br />\n<br />\n天光啦，終於入市中心啦！拖住個喼搭兩個站去Baker Street，梗係唔可以錯過Sherlock Holmes Museum啦！去到未開門，但係已經有好多遊客排緊隊買飛，旗袍妹都唔輸蝕排埋一份。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LqkNV9B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLqkNV9B.jpg&h=d94ec8fc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n旗袍妹弱質纖纖，幾經辛苦先至搬到個喼入屋，點知轉過頭⋯⋯<br />\n&quot;Sorry, I'm afraid we don't have enough space for your suitcase.&quot;<br />\n咁即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&ldquo;Perhaps you could store it at the nearest train station.&quot;<br />\n乜英國佬咁絕情㗎咩？點算好，仲有5個鐘先可以check-in airbnb，平時呢啲嘢不嬲係旗袍爸負責⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WP8LJbg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWP8LJbg.png&h=8c3bb6d1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n已經冇玩PKGO好耐，但想捉隻香港冇嘅小丑，嚟到幾個鐘已經捉到唔想捉。 <br />\n<br />\n其實倫敦街頭好多紀念品店都提供寄存服務，貴就貴咗啲，不過去到有用嘅時候就唔同講法啦。點都好，俾個鬼婆搞到燥燥地，點都要面全面撤退先，橫掂留喺倫敦五日，之後再返嚟都唔遲。<br />\n<br />\n於是去咗大英博物館先，咁啱隔離就有間可以寄存行李嘅舖頭，&pound;5/5個鐘，好乸脷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上次嚟倫敦因為有旗袍媽同埋旗袍妹妹，所以最尾冇去到。今次仲可以自己一個周圍睇，仲唔睇個夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然好癡漢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O4dvUno.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO4dvUno.jpg&h=7ac71a8c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9f1QUnj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9f1QUnj.jpg&h=4223d969&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gtj7b81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGtj7b81.jpg&h=c12fc069&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TN2P9Ss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTN2P9Ss.jpg&h=51385ac8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HQ9fkY9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHQ9fkY9.jpg&h=afd7a3f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n博物館以國家為單位，一個國家一個zone，你對邊啲國家冇性趣就可以直接skip。唔使入場費之餘，仲會有義工帶zone tour，講解得好詳細，你問旗袍妹印度教唔同神像象徵乜嘢，旗袍妹依家都搭到你。最抵讚嘅係，除咗zone tour之外，有時仲會有義工好似深水埗擺地攤咁款，俾遊客親手摸古董，更有專人深入講解背後嘅故事。就係呢度，旗袍妹同個義工婆婆討論咗好耐關於中、韓、印嘅歷史。唯一挑剔嘅係冇得坐低慢慢傾。<br />\n<br />\n你可能會問，博物館又大又免費，點會冇強國人？答案係有嘅，但其實嚟得博物館嘅，一係遊學團，一係教育水平奇高嘅，一個嚟買名牌嘅大媽又點會咁有文化。講到呢度，我喺個地攤都見到個讀博物館學嘅中國留學生，佢話第一次見到華人好開心，即刻捉咗旗袍妹去做訪問。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fccc7Eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFccc7Eb.jpg&h=45e28801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cQ7HLqT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcQ7HLqT.jpg&h=cf161a7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最多中國遊客睇嘅，就係呢兩幅畫卷。當年看守莫高窟藏經洞嘅道士低價賤賣畫卷俾番鬼佬，輾轉流落歐洲各大博物館，大英博物館就係其中之一。<br />\n<br />\n前人輕蔑文化傳承，堅守中華傳統文化嘅旗袍妹都當仁不讓，不禁義憤填膺。但係，最令旗袍妹慚愧嘅係，旗袍妹冇付諸行動，只將文學院放A2，甚至俾旗袍媽再調後去A3。雖然依家旗袍媽好開心，我都叫做「尊親」，俾佢出面喺啲朋友面前威下，但係旗袍妹依家對住科A1，後悔莫及，只可以搖頭嘆息。"},{"pid":"db211bac992f8fc5f44ec4f6f119f10ae6b10de7","tid":1133885,"uid":65439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T18:03:25.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"b6918a611f7d309fb0a858c8aa5e34b5a6cc8ecd","tid":1133885,"uid":62721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T18:26:12.000Z","msg":"Nice <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f196e180c4ed018c552549e2f115b568d2929141","tid":1133885,"uid":186051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T18:46:56.000Z","msg":"留名 樓主加油<br />\n咁快完sem 我仲要考final<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b01e94b33b840a279427d05fb3ed23e43065dc4c","tid":1133885,"uid":186051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T18:48:48.000Z","msg":"留名 樓主加油<br />\n<br />\n咁快完sem 我仲要考final <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3176ebf7731c64e27868d3fb0628b56574e8fa2a","tid":1133885,"uid":16376,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T18:52:20.000Z","msg":"個POST睇得好辛苦"},{"pid":"a13f33fdce78c176c255476437a9cc0443bb5aa5","tid":1133885,"uid":114275,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T23:54:26.000Z","msg":"推 希望你搵到知音 <br />\n<br />\n只係太文藝本人其實承受不了"},{"pid":"1ca9ae8b44fcb1b7e88a405bf7a468d2ab46062e","tid":1133885,"uid":80814,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T02:03:58.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得旅遊Blog要好似樓主咁, 多啲自己對遊覽景點嘅經歷同感受先好睇, 得啲圖無詳細描述真係睇完都唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5600187a7a62a3f6839f7162f2d26519edc72474","tid":1133885,"uid":229609,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T02:08:52.000Z","msg":"說來慚愧,咁大個人淨係去過台灣,亦都未試過一個人去旅行。<br />\n老喇!真羨慕你地後生嗰種行動力與勇氣,呢d野我一早就失去哂......"},{"pid":"2133ccec3a1c9536633b043e0838dd312fbb7054","tid":1133885,"uid":119433,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T02:18:22.000Z","msg":"BGM:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=inC7AvkblBQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DinC7AvkblBQ&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgELPkHgDHOcRHwLuXI7BMvHI%3D&h=8726fe66\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=inC7AvkblBQ</a><br />\n<br />\n「旅館寒燈獨不眠，客心何事轉悽然？<br />\n故鄉今夜思千里，霜鬢明朝又一年。」<br />\n<br />\n行咗四個幾鐘大英博物館，係時候夠鐘去airbnb check-in啦。雖然有兩個Underground站距離，但旗袍妹喺香港係行路撚，所以拖住喼行咗十五分鐘就到。<br />\n<br />\n旗袍妹有諗過慳返啲盤川住youth hostel，但係旗袍妹頹摺毒，不善交際，一句起兩句止，費事影衰香港人個朵，都係自摺住單人房算。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9rbp1Qf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9rbp1Qf.jpg&h=44417388&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n間airbnb座落於南亞區，企理係企理，但成日一返到房就成浸咖喱味。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nq6acWX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnq6acWX.jpg&h=b5f46ad3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAirbnb樓下間餐廳係N君嘅名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n擺低行李，四點幾，決定返返去Sherlock Holmes Museum，順便早啲食飯早啲瞓覺，畢竟馬不停蹄咗咁多個鐘頭。一入到去，又係嗰個烹我扯嘅鬼婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &quot;Oh, you've stored your luggage!&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wnm5Mg4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwnm5Mg4.jpg&h=9308ccf1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n盛惠&pound;15，入到去得兩層，仲細過我屋企。入到去又浸嗡味，唔掂得，唔坐得，要等齊成group人先走得。旗袍妹去過咁多度旅行，挨過咁多苦，平時唔講粗口，呢間真係要屌。<br />\n<br />\n原本睇咗google map想行去食burger &amp; lobster，但係行咗兩個街口見到有fish &amp; chips，即刻狗衝入去食。上次嚟基本上餐餐都要就旗袍媽，唔係食中餐就係自己煮，都冇食過英國嘢（唔好理好唔好食先）。不過呢間fish &amp; chips味道唔講啦，你見旗袍妹連相都冇影就知。<br />\n<br />\n入夜，英國人準時五點收工，仲早過香港人。來生真係要做歐洲人。百貨公司可能會開到八九點，但係唯一開到聽朝嘅就係酒吧。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N7TTaXY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN7TTaXY.jpg&h=ef4a56c6&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/69SphCZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F69SphCZ.jpg&h=d248125a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n獨自漫步街頭，人來人往，但係一個熟悉嘅靈魂都冇。<br />\n<br />\n返到airbnb，沖完涼，突然喺度思考人生：點解我會喺呢個世界上？我喺呢個世界做緊咩？點解人要有同伴？愛究竟係乜？我愛嘅係邊個？又有邊個愛我？如果我唔喺呢個世界上，呢個世界會點？望一望周圍，嗰盞眨下眨下嘅檯燈，嗰罐半空嘅Guinness，嗰隻Paddington Bear，甚或身邊寂寞嘅空氣，都答我唔到。算啦，瞓啦柒頭。<br />\n<br />\nDay 1 總計：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5YCHOOX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5YCHOOX.png&h=4a664ea4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1bc8b5ae193097b98584387ec65e8430c3b98951","tid":1133885,"uid":160579,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T04:48:30.000Z","msg":"支持樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 文學愛好者here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好欣賞樓主咁有心機，睇得出文學修養幾高<br />\n諗返起之前去過兩次英國嘅回憶，俾你搞到好想solo去一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n八卦問吓，樓主讀緊咩科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c283f9d32f0b13f38ab4533c360713852e93f16","tid":1133885,"uid":119433,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1bc8b5ae193097b98584387ec65e8430c3b98951","tid":1133885,"uid":160579,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T04:48:30.000Z","msg":"支持樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 文學愛好者here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好欣賞樓主咁有心機，睇得出文學修養幾高<br />\n諗返起之前去過兩次英國嘅回憶，俾你搞到好想solo去一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n八卦問吓，樓主讀緊咩科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:01:25.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n私人嘢唔自爆啦，有興趣可tg：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/qipaomui\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fqipaomui&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgELPkHgDHOcRHwLuXI7BMvHI%3D&h=c0229a93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/qipaomui</a>"},{"pid":"cd8e0e9cfa6e862740ad55704c8be65358e21750","tid":1133885,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T12:12:20.000Z","msg":"想扑旗袍妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />妹"},{"pid":"c54342b88fac5d62327c9dd385dbc68b0ec8ea77","tid":1133885,"uid":31962,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T13:25:52.000Z","msg":"20歲寫野咁老成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02779403007000354161de38da15083f165029fd","tid":1133885,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T16:32:17.000Z","msg":"歐洲wifi好方便 我覺得唔洗上網卡"},{"pid":"385dd40fd6ede670c5b1a54579aa2869f35a6351","tid":1133885,"uid":119433,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T04:42:22.000Z","msg":"BGM:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hQpdqTl9HLg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhQpdqTl9HLg&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgELPkHgDHOcRHwLuXI7BMvHI%3D&h=113fdd62\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hQpdqTl9HLg</a><br />\n<br />\n一日之計在於晨，七點幾就自然醒。喺香港旗袍妹一定瞓到日上三竿。喺pantry食咗公家cereal<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇盤川係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T5Vm7ay.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT5Vm7ay.jpg&h=4b610cac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KCeZTQo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKCeZTQo.jpg&h=ad85da09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n影完呢兩張相之後，跟住落嚟嗰十日冇一日好天嘅。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JLqqPoy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJLqqPoy.jpg&h=e895b3cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去咗Canal Museum、Postal Museum同埋Charles Dickens Museum，影咗唯一一張相。呢個set盛惠&pound;10，唔好睇佢細細份，旗袍妹淨係飲碗湯都飽哂。碗湯好似話跟返Dickens家族嘅傳統方法煮，香甜得嚟又唔膩！個lemon drizzle啱哂旗袍妹呢啲死港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n查實旗袍妹第二日要飛愛丁堡，但係搭Ryanair，所以要將件大喼寄存，淨係帶細喼北上。所以就要返返airbnb攞行李，寄八日，咁就冇咗&pound;40<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n夜晚8:00約咗姑媽一家喺Canary Wharf 食牛扒，所以順便去Greenwich Observatory。搭Underground要去到Canary Wharf轉DLR輕鐵。旗袍妹唔係大西北人，人生淨係搭過一次輕鐵，唔係咁知點俾錢，不自覺地上咗車。咁細架車廂竟然都有個嬸嬸check飛！呢個時候先知大獲。<br />\n&quot;Your Oyster card please <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&quot;<br />\n嘟完之後⋯⋯<br />\n&quot;Your card doesn't have enough money. Do you have a credit card?&quot;<br />\n俾佢碌咗&pound;5.6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hDqm7ag.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhDqm7ag.jpg&h=a8b86d5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/504i9oE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F504i9oE.jpg&h=3745fde6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n子午線一錘定音，全人類都要跟。區區一條線，定義咗全世界任何一個角落嘅時間。日換星移，海枯石爛，量化時間真係咁緊要？點解時間一定要工整地由一分一秒計算？細個嘅時候，旗袍妹好想時間過得快啲，快啲變大人，唔使再俾旗袍爸旗袍媽因為成績唔好而鬧。去到二十歲，旗袍妹又好想校慢隻錶，因為，以前做學生妹只需要擔心學業(according to 旗袍媽)，依家，事業、人際、愛情，通通冇老師教旗袍妹，冇得補習，冇標準答案⋯⋯邊夠時間逐一尋覓？路漫漫其修遠兮。<br />\n<br />\n五點鐘，去到出口，成排員工列隊等我一個收工。呢個時候先知時間嘅重要性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有三個鐘，點消磨好？旗袍妹飲完湯之後就冇再食過嘢，加埋落雨濕凍，成身打哂冷震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好彩個樣仲算後生，可以入University of Greenwich搵個位嘆暖氣用wifi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XLG5PoQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXLG5PoQ.jpg&h=d85fcb67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TZmQ0vs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTZmQ0vs.jpg&h=9e94601f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇怕呢餐應該喺成程最豪最好食嘅一餐㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平時自己一個邊會食得咁富貴<br />\n<br />\nDay 2 總計：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H2AZfoG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH2AZfoG.png&h=704a82ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41ccec0be63102a278ad3e0b250730e3f413114c","tid":1133885,"uid":95314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T11:15:24.000Z","msg":"sad 呢排都諗緊人生意義"},{"pid":"8791496e964405b673565fce750319f87459211d","tid":1133885,"uid":186051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T19:33:04.000Z","msg":"留名 樓主加油<br />\n咁快完sem去旅行 我仲要考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa5554f9acb7a10eab62a57f83c7c58c41ce247","tid":1133885,"uid":19310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T02:56:42.000Z","msg":"Canal Museum可唔可以寫多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外Postal Museum冇坐Mailrail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d598138897fee97ac5456f5d2fead0e5b90bd82","tid":1133885,"uid":119433,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T06:20:01.000Z","msg":"BGM:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ALNHoEtiDJs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DALNHoEtiDJs&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgELPkHgDHOcRHwLuXI7BMvHI%3D&h=c1a41313\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ALNHoEtiDJs</a><br />\n<br />\n「那些與你毫無關係的人，就是毫無關係的，永遠是毫無關係的。<br />\n從認識的第一天開始，其實你就知道。<br />\n就算是笑得甜甜蜜蜜，就算是有過無關痛癢的來往，就算你努力經營這段關係。<br />\n而那些與你有關的，就是與你有關的，是逃也逃不掉的，就算你們只見過三次，就算你們三年彼此才搭理一次，就算是你簡直想不起他或她的樣子，就算是你們隔著十萬八千里。<br />\n有些人注定是你生命裡的癌症，而有些人只是一個噴嚏而已。<br />\n這一切，據說都是『因了冥冥之中的緣份』。」<br />\n<br />\n上回講到，影完King's Cross 同 St. Pancras，之後都冇再出過日頭。迷濛中漫步，倫敦人著哂乾濕褸，已經見慣不怪。Canal Museum 都幾隔涉，喺正幾個Underground站中間，好彩本身旗袍妹係行路撚，如果帶旗袍媽嚟一定搞唔掂。<br />\n<br />\n一入到去，半個人影都冇。原來個南亞售票員人有三急，等咗5分鐘先買到飛。正價&pound;5，學生減&pound;1。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zyRh16w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzyRh16w.jpg&h=165fd053&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JfYsETc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJfYsETc.jpg&h=a77db398&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n150年前，倫敦人用呢個人工運河網絡由挪威引入冰塊。一個意大利人喺自己國家走投無路，拋妻棄子嚟倫敦盡地一鋪，租咗運河旁邊一間屋開始整雪糕。唔使幾年，佢已經發咗達。間屋就係博物館前身。<br />\n<br />\n呢個世界，唔係個個好似嗰個意大利人咁好彩，結合天時地利人和，遇到有心嘅倫敦人，逆轉人生。150年後，有個來自香港嘅憤青，自細俾咗老一輩湊大，得唔到父母嘅關愛，所以希望有異性可以照顧佢。佢唔奢望長相廝守，呢一刻盡興而返便足夠。中學時期讀齋校，加上唯一目標係入u，所以忽略咗呢一方面嘅需要；好啦，入咗u，下一步要點做？唔知啊，上下莊先，keep住自己忙到停唔到先。咁依家落咗莊，要做啲咩呢？<br />\n<br />\n直至佢遇到N君。<br />\n<br />\n「你呢排好謝 你唔好咁夜瞓啊❤️」<br />\n「唔好病😢」<br />\n「今個禮拜出去飲喜茶好冇？😆」<br />\n<br />\n不知呢啲係「生命裡的癌症」，定係「一個噴嚏而已」？佢同N係「毫無關係」，定係「因了冥冥之中的緣份」？識咗三個月，佢到依家都唔知。<br />\n<br />\n睇咗冇耐，就有班小朋友鴨仔團擁咗入嚟，毒撚見光死，即刻入廁所避一避，順便釋放一下今朝嘅cereal。"},{"pid":"789b186a9a206b8cbd9af9b4888b5519b72fd43c","tid":1133885,"uid":119433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"faa5554f9acb7a10eab62a57f83c7c58c41ce247","tid":1133885,"uid":19310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T02:56:42.000Z","msg":"Canal Museum可唔可以寫多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外Postal Museum冇坐Mailrail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:38:49.000Z","msg":"冇啊，賣飛嗰度講到好恐怖咁，唔敢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a1a99f2635ede904f24cb98ac0555a1c8a610b","tid":1133885,"uid":81106,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T08:29:08.000Z","msg":"絲打年紀細細，文采難得好好，亦有留意唔少八九十年代流行文化，好難得，留名支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只係阿叔覺得有少少強說愁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}